social_posts.post_text: Some seriously delicious Christmas Eve morning goodies from @theodoresfinefoods YUM! Hope you are having an amazing day!
Merry Christmas 2022!

Isn't it normal that when a friend gives you a beautiful bottle of champagne, your first thought is....ooooo, it's so pretty, I can't wait to style it! Just me? Oh well, thanks so much, Jess!! I can't wait to drink it now that I've styled it! Happy New Year! Here's to 2023!

I'm excited to share something new coming to the Hidden Valley Farmhouse! Some of you may remember I previously had booths at both an antique store and a gift store. When I closed them, all the treasures were packed up, but it's time to list them and share them with you!! I'll be posting all these vintage and decor treasures over the next few weeks, along with some amazing things from my personal collection! Watch for notifications of the first sale this weekend! What would love to see??

I am so excited to share some treasures with you later this morning, at 9am (MST)!!

Here are some important details about the sale:

1. Please DM me with the item number or numbers you would like to purchase, this is your commitment to purchase. I will confirm your purchase/availability.

2. Upon confirmation of sale, please send your email address and mailing address for shipping

3. An invoice, including shipping, will be sent via Paypal and must be paid within 24 hours.

4. Items will be shipped within 5 business days from date of payment via USPS or UPS.

Thank you for joining me and enjoying some treasure hunting fun! Keep an eye out for the next sale soon with some ironstone and butter pats!

These three amazing humans made me a mom and were the answer to my deepest prayers. They are loving, kind, funny, and smart and bring me endless amounts of joy!! I am so very grateful for each of them and still can't believe they call me Mom ♥️
Welcome to the farmhouse, Otis...our new sweet boy! He is a little guy with so much personality, and we are definitely in love!

120 people EVERY DAY. Imagine for a minute losing that many people in your world; from your job, your neighborhood, your child's school, because their life was lost to gun violence. Just imagine every pair of shoes in this photo had a person you know in them.  No matter your political party or stance on guns, we have to agree that this has to STOP! We can find a way to support gun rights and common sense laws that protect people in this country! 🧡

It isn't too early for the magic of the Christmas tree, especially any tree from @kingofchristmas 

We've added a new tree to the farmhouse, this 6.5' King Fraser Fir is absolutely STUNNING! It has 600 pre-strung LED lights and a power pole for the easiest setup ever. It also has a remote control with dimmable lights! I'm not quite ready for Christmas decorations, but this beauty is decorated for fall and makes me happy! I'll transition it to my traditional Thanksgiving tree soon! Do you do a fall or Thanksgiving tree?

#kingofchristmastrees #kingofchristmas
#christmastree #magicoftheseason

My new @kingofchristmas tree gets a makeover today! I will say, I really do love the tradition of a Thanksgiving tree...all the twinkle along with the fall goodness! I hope you had a wonderful Thanksgiving with family and friends! Now...let's bring on Christmas!!

#kingofchristmastrees #kingofchristmas #thanksgivingdecor #thanksgivingtree #thanksgiving

Layers of twinkle and magic with the most amazing Christmas tree from @kingofchristmas  My vibe this year is a moody christmas, and this is definitely my favorite ever! If you don't have a tree you LOVE...you need to get one from King of Christmas. Every year, they are stunning and absolutely perfect!
